      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Secure an Advantage[/i] +edge by dancing for an audience, add +1 and take +2 momentum on a hit. On a strong hit, also add +2 (one time only) if you make a move to interact with someone in the audience.\"
    }
  },
  
  {
    \"skill\" : {
      \"check\":\"false\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Face Danger[/i] +edge in a fight by nimbly avoiding your foe's attacks, add +1 and take +1 momentum on a hit.\"
    }
  },
  
  {
    \"skill\" : {
      \"check\":\"false\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you or an ally make a progress move and roll a hit, you may perform a dance to commemorate the event. If you do, roll +edge. On a [b]strong hit[/b], you and each of your allies may take +2 momentum and +1 spirit. On a [b]weak hit[/b], you take +1 momentum or +1 spirit, but your allies are unmoved.\"
    }
  }
  
]"
